Winner Stays
Ringan Ledwidge
“Winner Stays” for Nike by Ringan Ledwidge & Wieden sees a friendly, generic game of Winner Stays between some kids in a park turn into a famous footballer-filled epic match. The children turn into the famous players; Ronaldo, Neymar, Rooney et al. as they each tap the ball, as the changes happen the crescendo builds until the players risk everything to win.
